#. Id: 50921-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 0.0
#. -- Parent line: -
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Iyo University Dialogue
#: 50921-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid ""
"Keep loitering our aisles, /OUTLANDER/, and you'll end up trampled by sleep "
"deprived scientists... What brings you to World's End University? Do you "
"need something?"
msgstr ""
"繼續在我們的過道遊蕩, /OUTLANDER/, 那些徹夜不眠的科學家會蹂躪你的... 你來世界"
"盡頭的大學幹嘛來的? 你需要些什麼嘛?"

#. Id: 50924-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (50921-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Iyo University Dialogue
#: 50924-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Can you tell me about this place?"
msgstr "能給我講講這個地方麼?"

#. Id: 50929-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 2.0
#. -- Parent line: 1 (50924-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Iyo University Dialogue
#: 50929-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid ""
"Here we study and analyse lost tech from the ancient world, slowly but "
"surely we're uncovering the secrets of our forgotten history. The problem is "
"that most ruins have already been scavenged, making it difficult to develop "
"accurate theories without solid evidence... "
msgstr ""
"我們在這裏研究和分析舊世界的遺落科技, 雖然緩慢, 可確實在揭示我們那段被遺忘的"
"曆史中的秘密. 問題是大部分的遺跡都被盜掘了, 使得在沒有實物證明的情形下發掘出"
"精準無誤的理論很困難... "

#. Id: 50951-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (50929-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Iyo University Dialogue
#: 50951-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid ""
"So, that's where our tech hunters come in. They scour the unexplored lands "
"for any possible remains we can use in our research... If you're interested "
"in adventuring, our stores pay good money for relics. Make sure you bring "
"anything you find to us, okay?"
msgstr ""
"因此, 需要我們的科技獵人. 他們會為了任何可供我們研究的殘骸去搜索他人未經之"
"地... 如果你喜愛冒險, 我們的商店會出高價購買古代遺物. 一定把任何你找到的東西"
"帶給我們, 好嗎?"

#. Id: 50939-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.0
#. -- Parent line: 3 (50951-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Iyo University Dialogue
#: 50939-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Sure, I'll bear that in mind."
msgstr "當然, 我會記得的."

#. Id: 50945-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.0
#. -- Parent line: 4 (50939-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Iyo University Dialogue
#: 50945-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Great. Now, if that's everything, I've got work to do..."
msgstr "太好了. 現在, 如果沒有其他事情了, 我還有工作要做..."

#. Id: 50940-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.0
#. -- Parent line: 3 (50951-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Iyo University Dialogue
#: 50940-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Actually I'm no adventurer. But thanks for the info."
msgstr "事實上我並不是冒險者. 但還是謝謝你提供的信息."

#. Id: 50946-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.0
#. -- Parent line: 4 (50940-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Iyo University Dialogue
#: 50946-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "You're welcome. Now, if that's everything, I've got work to do..."
msgstr "別客氣. 現在, 如果沒有其他事情了, 我還有工作要做..."

#. Id: 50948-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 2.0
#. -- Parent line: 1 (50924-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Iyo University Dialogue
#. -- Condition: Who: TARGET, Condition: IS_SAME_RACE_AS_ME=1, Tag: -1
#. -- Condition: Target Race(s): Skeleton
#: 50948-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid ""
"Here we study and analyse lost tech from the ancient world to uncover the "
"secrets of our history. Most of the ruins have already been scavenged, "
"making it difficult to develop accurate theories without solid evidence... "
msgstr ""
"我們在這裏研究和分析舊世界的遺落科技以此揭示我們曆史的秘密. 大部分的遺跡都被"
"盜掘了, 使得在沒有實物證明的情形下發掘出精準無誤的理論很困難... "

#. Id: 50952-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (50948-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Iyo University Dialogue
#: 50952-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid ""
"So our tech hunters scour the unexplored lands for any possible remains we "
"can use in our research, but most of it needs to go through me first... If "
"you're an adventurer looking to sell relics, just make sure you bring them "
"to our stores rather than elsewhere, okay?"
msgstr ""
"因此我們的科技獵人為了任何可供研究的殘骸去搜索未經之地, 不過大部分都需要經由"
"我手... 如果你是個企圖販賣遺物的冒險者, 一定把它們帶來我們的商店而不是其他的"
"地方, 好嗎?"

#. Id: 50923-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (50921-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Iyo University Dialogue
#: 50923-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "I had some questions about your work..."
msgstr "我對你的工作有些疑問..."

#. Id: 50926-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 2.0
#. -- Parent line: 1 (50923-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Iyo University Dialogue
#: 50926-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid ""
"Did you have something specific in mind? There's not a great deal of "
"information I can enlighten you with that hasn't already been documented in "
"our records..."
msgstr ""
"你還記著什麼特別的線索嗎? 鑒於我們的文庫裏沒有已經記錄在案的文檔, 我無法據此"
"向你闡明更多的信息..."

#. Id: 50927-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (50926-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Iyo University Dialogue
#: 50927-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Can you teach me about world history?"
msgstr "可以給我講述一下世界的曆史麼?"

#. Id: 50930-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.0
#. -- Parent line: 3 (50927-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Iyo University Dialogue
#: 50930-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid ""
"With all due respect, /OUTLANDER/, asking me to sum up the history of the "
"world is not much different to asking a doctor to teach you medicine in ten "
"minutes. On top of that, many scientists have different theories on events. "
"I suggest you browse through our library if you're interested to know more."
msgstr ""
"恕我直言, /OUTLANDER/, 請我給你講述世界曆史無異於讓醫生在十分鍾內教你藥理. 再"
"者, 不同的科學家對事物的理論闡述也不盡相同. 如果你想知道更多世界曆史, 我建議"
"你瀏覽我們的圖書館."

#. Id: 50943-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.0
#. -- Parent line: 4 (50930-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Iyo University Dialogue
#. Id: 48795-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (48726-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Swamp Barman
#: 50943-Dialogue.mod:0 48795-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Okay, thanks for the info."
msgstr "好吧, 謝謝你的信息."

#. Id: 50931-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (50926-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Iyo University Dialogue
#: 50931-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "The Holy Nation talk of a First Extinction. What do you know of it?"
msgstr "聖國那邊聽說的第一次滅絕. 你都知道些什麼?"

#. Id: 50933-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.0
#. -- Parent line: 3 (50931-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Iyo University Dialogue
#: 50933-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid ""
"The First Extinction? I personally believe it to be a plague epidemic, but "
"Mr Finch stands firmly by it being a 'freak tornado'. Whatever it was, it "
"appears that the skeleton was better equipped to survive it. But, human "
"nature is to scapegoat, in particular those that are different to them... "
msgstr ""
"第一次滅絕? 我個人認為那是一次瘟疫蔓延, 但是芬奇先生堅持認為是'巨大海嘯'. 不"
"管是什麼導致的, 骨人顯然做好了生存的準備. 可是, 愛找替罪羊是人類的天性, 尤其"
"是對那些與自己不同的種族... "

#. Id: 50953-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.0
#. -- Parent line: 4 (50933-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Iyo University Dialogue
#: 50953-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid ""
"Our physical differences, in a time of panic and turmoil, only provoke "
"further fear and clinging to ideas of blame. Hence the condemnation of my "
"kind as playing a part in the downfall by the Holy Nation."
msgstr ""
"由於我們身體構造上的差異, 一段時間的慌亂和騷動, 隻會引發更進一步的恐懼和持續"
"的指責. 因此聖國宣告我的種族有罪也算是帝國隕落的一部分."

#. Id: 50932-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (50926-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Iyo University Dialogue
#: 50932-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid ""
"You existed way back to the ancient times, right? Can't you remember "
"anything?"
msgstr "你從遠古時代存活至今, 對嗎? 你什麼都記不得麼?"

#. Id: 50936-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.0
#. -- Parent line: 3 (50932-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Iyo University Dialogue
#: 50936-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid ""
"The memory of a skeleton is not as long lasting as our bodies, "
"unfortunately. I don't even remember if I existed within the ancient race, "
"or not. Trust me, it is highly frustrating for a theorist to have possibly "
"existed at the very time period they are dedicated to investigating."
msgstr ""
"骨人的記憶並不像我們的身軀這樣長久, 這很不幸. 我甚至都不記得自己是不是在古老"
"的種族內生活過. 相信我, 這對於一個致力於調查自己可能存在過的時代的理論工作者"
"來說極其的沮喪."

#. Id: 50934-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (50926-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Iyo University Dialogue
#: 50934-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "What happened to the ancients? And how did we come to be?"
msgstr "古人怎麼了? 我們如何形成的?"

#. Id: 50935-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.0
#. -- Parent line: 3 (50934-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Iyo University Dialogue
#: 50935-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid ""
"Mr Finch believes all organics to be direct descendants of smaller tribes "
"outside of the ancient society. And the ancients? We think they would have "
"lived disconnected from the rest of the world, a deadly disease could have "
"killed them off while leaving the skeletons and other tribes unnaffected. "
"But, again, there are many different theories on how we all came to be..."
msgstr ""
"芬奇先生認為所有的有機生物都是遠古社會中外來部族的直係後代. 然後古人嘛? 我們"
"認為他們與世隔絕地生活著, 一場致命的疾病把他們殺光了, 而骨人和其他部族沒有受"
"到影響. 但是, 需要重申, 關於我們如何形成的有其他不同的理論..."

#. Id: 50941-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (50926-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Iyo University Dialogue
#: 50941-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Records? Where can I find these?"
msgstr "記錄? 我可以在哪裏找到這些?"

#. Id: 50942-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.0
#. -- Parent line: 3 (50941-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Iyo University Dialogue
#: 50942-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Just take a look around the library. You'll find them."
msgstr "隻要去看看圖書館. 你就會發現它們."

#. Id: 53280-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (50926-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Iyo University Dialogue
#: 53280-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Know where I can find any Ancient Science books?"
msgstr "你知道我能去哪裏找些古代科技書籍嗎?"

#. Id: 53281-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.0
#. -- Parent line: 3 (53280-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Iyo University Dialogue
#: 53281-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid ""
"... You're an adventurer?... Forgive me, but freely passing out tips to our "
"competition will land me in a great deal of trouble with Mr Finch. Try "
"talking to the Tech Hunters over in the World's End bar."
msgstr ""
"... 如果你是個冒險者?... 請原諒, 隻是芬奇先生會因為我把這些消息免費分發給競爭"
"對手而讓我受盡苦頭. 去跟世界盡頭酒吧的科技獵人談談吧."

#. Id: 50928-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 2.0
#. -- Parent line: 1 (50923-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Iyo University Dialogue
#. -- Condition: Who: TARGET, Condition: IS_SAME_RACE_AS_ME=1, Tag: -1
#. -- Condition: Target Race(s): Skeleton
#: 50928-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid ""
"Look, you don't need to worry... no one will ever know the truth. As long as "
"I am Finch's second in command, I will see to that myself."
msgstr ""
"你看, 你沒必要擔心... 沒人會知道真相. 隻要我依舊是芬奇的二把手, 我就會自己解"
"決問題."

#. Id: 50950-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (50928-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Iyo University Dialogue
#: 50950-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Let's not waste eachother's time with this act any more."
msgstr "我們別再為此浪費彼此的時間了."

#~ msgid "Nothing, nevermind."
#~ msgstr "沒事, 別介意."
